腺炎等等，都讓體重下降。運動過度，體力消耗太大，體重也是下降。"},{"pid":"ba6917656ad98a38a937a2744d689adb99d7d178","tid":331573,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:02:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無胃口食野</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n無特別食少 但清淡咗就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab23af4edf2b259495fdafecc4a5451d76707f42","tid":331573,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為 天增歲月人燒瘦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf18cd65b0a32c215d433ce890465de605c15322","tid":331573,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發燒令你產生幻覺<br />\n睇錯瘦咗2kg 其實係肥咗20kg</blockquote><br />\n咁就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ee1e91dd76dfbf33b38fb1d6b97c2e6747b16e","tid":331573,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:04:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>體溫上升 新陳代謝增速</blockquote><br />\n都增得好快吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4188e2e4a1de3547fdef46b9e36f449ee58ebedb","tid":331573,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:05:01.000Z","msg":"脂肪(勢能)&gt;發燒(熱能)<br />\n你d脂肪拎晒去發熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9334bc12dd5ce97770c3e26c00f39ba2b32ef6","tid":331573,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:05:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發燒會讓體重下降，不論是感染、癌症、中風，抑或是代謝疾病導致的發燒，都讓體重減輕，因為人體體溫上升，基礎代謝率就增加，每增加體溫1℃，基礎代謝率增加7%，而且發燒時常有噁心吃不下飯，脫水，蛋白質分解速率增加，讓體重下降得更快。<br />\n<br />\n除了心臟衰竭，還有慢性感染，不論是慢性氣管炎、慢性腎盂腎炎、慢性前列腺炎等等，都讓體重下降。運動過度，體力消耗太大，體重也是下降。</blockquote><br />\n要瘦真係好簡單<br />\n啲肥婆成日嘈嘈嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaae0d7e18726e887bfe895fe05080edb8d0fcdd","tid":33157